content:
This build was released on the 28th of August, 2023.

General Changes:
 - Fixed duplicate stars.
 - Fixed some crashes.
 - Readded Captain Fly Guy.
 - Added silver star mission in Grassy Highlands
 - Re-enabled post credits ACT 1 mode
 - Tweaked Cave Dungeon.
 - Backflip now unlocks at 2/3 red stars as intended.
 - Fixed Dream Tower cage collision.
 - Fixed stars going OOB from level scaling.
 - Better water camea.
 - Some AI trolling.
 - Added music corruptions.
